<html>
<head>
  <title>Service unavailable</title>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Service unavailable</h1>

  <p>
  System is currenly in maintainance mode and unavailable. Please try again
  later. In case you have some questions regarding the portal functionality,
  please ask the portal administrator.
  </p>

  <p>
  Note: this message was not caused by a system error and will disappear right
  after the maintainance operations complete.
  </p>

  <p>We apologise for inconvenience.</p>

  <em>NauDoc version &dtml-productVersion;</em>
</body>
</html>
